dc_title_s: Map of the Counties of Salem and Gloucester New Jersey 1848
dc_description_s: Sheet 2: Gloucester County from Deptford Township to Harrison Township. Map shows Deptford, Harrison, and East Greenwich. Also shows a plan of the town of Salem. |Sheet 3: Salem County from Mannington to Lower Alloway Creek. Map shows municipalities of Lower Penns Neck, Mannington, Pilesgrove, Elsinborough, Upper Alloways Creek, Lower Alloways Creek.
